memory_text = "LEENA SHAH: 'Ignore the screen. Ask them their name, then ask whoever came with them.' A porter says the computer has renamed Bed Four for the third time. Leena tears labels from the printer and writes by hand: name, medicine, witness. 'If nobody knows, write unknown. Do not guess.'"
